WEBVTT

00:00:01.973 --> 00:00:06.535
Autism is something
that many people know about.

00:00:07.570 --> 00:00:09.890
For example, some people think

00:00:09.914 --> 00:00:14.440
that autistic people
are fair-skinned males

00:00:14.464 --> 00:00:16.519
that speak in monotone

00:00:16.543 --> 00:00:20.130
and constantly go on and on
about the same topic.

00:00:21.258 --> 00:00:26.252
Some people think that autistic people
do not know right from wrong,

00:00:26.276 --> 00:00:27.808
avoid attention

00:00:27.832 --> 00:00:31.832
and usually say the wrong thing
at the wrong time.